DateTime::Locale::dz_BT(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::dz_BT(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::dz_BT

SYNOPSIS

  use DateTime;

  my $dt = DateTime->now( locale => 'dz_BT' );
  print $dt->month_name();

DESCRIPTION

This is the DateTime locale package for Dzongkha Bhutan.

DATA

This locale inherits from the DateTime::Locale::dz locale.

It contains the following data.

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15
